Company Overview of Kodiak Capital Group, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Kodiak Capital Group, LLC is a private equity and venture capital firm specializing in growth equity investments, add-on acquisitions, convertible debt situations, recapitalization, buy and build strategies, lower middle market businesses, principal, and debt or equity investments. The firm focuses to invest in biotechnology, consumer products, life sciences, natural resources and social media technology industries. It also invests in publicly traded cannabis companies. It also seeks to invest in businesses with intangible value including brands or systems. The firm caters to businesses based in North America and may have overseas operations. It seeks to make equity investment of $1 million ...
Kodiak Capital Group, LLC is a private equity and venture capital firm specializing in growth equity investments, add-on acquisitions, convertible debt situations, recapitalization, buy and build strategies, lower middle market businesses, principal, and debt or equity investments. The firm focuses to invest in biotechnology, consumer products, life sciences, natural resources and social media technology industries. It also invests in publicly traded cannabis companies. It also seeks to invest in businesses with intangible value including brands or systems. The firm caters to businesses based in North America and may have overseas operations. It seeks to make equity investment of $1 million to $5 million in platform companies, where the revenue is between $5 million to $500 million and transaction size and EBITDA, each ranges between $1 million to $25 million. The firm co-invests with management to make non-control equity investments. Kodiak Capital Group, LLC was founded in 2009 and is based in Newport Beach, California with an additional office in San Diego, California.
